    {
      "id": "p005",
      "index": 5,
      "source": "At VLSI 2025, Cadence demonstrated their own UCIe-S die-to-die interconnect on N3E. Despite the node disadvantage, Intel has managed to best Cadence’s interconnect in data rate, channel length and shoreline bandwidth, only losing out in energy efficiency.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0257",
      "parent_block_index": 257,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "At VLSI 2025, Cadence demonstrated their own UCIe-S die-to-die interconnect on N3E. Despite the node disadvantage, Intel has managed to best Cadence’s interconnect in data rate, channel length and shoreline bandwidth, only losing out in energy efficiency.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "At VLSI 2025, Cadence demonstrated their own UCIe-S die-to-die interconnect on N3E. Despite the node disadvantage, Intel has managed to best Cadence’s interconnect in data rate, channel length and shoreline bandwidth, only losing out in energy efficiency.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 255,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "在 2025 年超大规模集成电路（VLSI）研讨会上，Cadence 展示了其基于 N3E 制程的 UCIe-S 裸片到裸片互连技术。尽管英特尔在制程节点上处于劣势，但其接口在数据速率、通道长度和单位边缘带宽方面均超越了 Cadence 的方案，仅在能效方面有所不及。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-18T22:51:31.645185",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        }
      },
      "confirmed": null,
